5:
Ugh, I'm sweating more than this
hog! Why's it so hot out here?!
14:
The heat will come down all the
more mercilessly if you keep
working yourself up like that.
19:
Grr! Forget it! I can barely think in
this heat! Alk, do something!
25:
I'm not a miracle worker. I can't just
summon a breeze with a snap of my
fingers...
28:
Wait, I see something up ahead.
Let's go take a look!
34: A pond! We've hit the jackpot!
39: Jump in, Alk! The water's great!
44:
Wh-whoa! Hold on, Kannon! You're
getting water all over me! And
you're, um...
48:
Huh? Why're you so worried about a
bit of water? C'mon! You'll thank me
later!
53:
Ahem. Before we go any further,
Kannon, you may want to look at
your clothes.
56:
My clothes? They're easy to move
around in and super cool to boot.
What's wrong with them?
60:
There's nothing wrong with your
garments, exactly, but you're not fit
to be seen in public now.
65:
What are you, my pops now? He's
always going on about how young
ladies should do this or that. As if
that matters for an adventurer!
69: Er, no. That's not what I mean, either—
72:
Then what do you mean? Alk, do you
get what he's saying?
74:
If you have something to say, spit it
out!
81:
Um... When you dove into the pond...
your clothes became... uh... more
form-fitting?
90:
E-excuse me?! Where were you
LOOKING?!
93:
I had no idea you were that kind of
person. You oughta be ashamed!
Pervert!
98:
Y-you were the one who jumped
into the water!
103:
I don't wanna hear it! Keep your
peepers on my face, buster, or else
I'll whoop your butt!
108:
I'm not looking at- at anything! I'm
not even looking in your direction!
112:
But you totally were before! Don't
deny it!
116:
Sigh... Is one peaceful day too much
to ask for?
